## Description {#details}

Generic binary error.

For errors that don&#39;t require their own specific sub-error (most errors) this class can be used to describe the error via a string message.

Definition at line 66 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/error-h">Error.h</a>.
